Author: dukeleto#7326
Content: @nobby BTCH inherits most/all features of KMD, but some features are related to the creation of the AC, specifically, the arguments that control all the options for the new AC

Author: dukeleto#7326
Content: when James and I created BTCH, there was no mining of AC's, and when we created BTCH, there was no CryptoConditions, so the current live chain does not have those features. If we recreated BTCH again, with these options, we would need to hardfork or maybe do a snapshot and airdrop onto the new chain to get those features.
